                {% endif %}
                {% if current_lang == "en-gb" %}
					<h5 class="wonder-is-col-h5">Quality guarantee</h5>
					<p class="wonder-is-col-p">Fertilizer production is controlled by an automation line, and the quality of the product is confirmed in a modern laboratory by qualified chemists.</p>
